401942,"uid":35749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:28:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每次揸車去到班馬線見到有人想過我就停低揮手叫佢地過，之後佢地好多都揮手多謝我，我心諗香港啲司機究竟點搞到啲行人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似揮手叫人過係不對的</blockquote><br />\n係，因為你讓唔代表你隔離條仆街會讓</blockquote><br />\n係，試過路口揮手叫人過俾隔離個fd屌<br />\n<br />\n佢話: 如果條友見你招手，佢就以為好安全就咁過，隔離有車衝出黎就撞撚死佢<br />\n<br />\n所以依家就寧願停定架車，等一陣人地就有意識你讓<br />\n佢行唔行就自己責任啦</blockquote><br />\n但如果係單線呢？"},{"pid":"d1a87fabe6b20176d7c697259c5d75f99712ba8e","tid":401942,"uid":137782,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:28:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登真係好多痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行人有優先權又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果睇住後面架車好近,唔通踩brake俾佢撞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當真係停俾你啦,後面架車撞埋嚟咪一樣會撞到班馬線嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係你開得太快囉撚樣"},{"pid":"fe9bfad9d08ae292b9004befa47634c89687a805","tid":401942,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:30:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登真係好多痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行人有優先權又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果睇住後面架車好近,唔通踩brake俾佢撞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當真係停俾你啦,後面架車撞埋嚟咪一樣會撞到班馬線嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係你開得太快囉撚樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non撚9"},{"pid":"37284ece961ad611bd79195bdd06fb0cde4eb245","tid":401942,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:31:30.000Z","msg":"1823"},{"pid":"047ce9df782f09ad071c9653f0a65317f802e050","tid":401942,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re